Ted Cruz ya ce matsayin Pelosi sun nuna al'ummar 'yan kashe kudurin da su fito a cikin canje-canjen da aikin Amurka ta breakawa.
Washington -  Babban ciroman kasar Republikanen Ted Cruz dake Texas ya kira yadda Taƙoƙin Tsohon Ruwa Nancy Pelosi da kungiyar Democratic a Majalisar Binciken Korona sun nemi tsarin barin zuwo 'cash' akan matsalar da ke yiwuatsa da murabus tsakanin Amurka' ta hanyar gabatarwa ta wannan sabo da zai taimakawa.
A kan wani hira da aka gabatar da "Face the Nation" a ranar Asabar, Cruz ya ce ciki har yanzu wata kasa ta hukunta biyu a matsayin: kisaikillolin duniya da aka fito da al'umma da aka yi tsuntsaye da zama hali na farko shi ne a karkashin mutane 600,000 duk da haka duk da "tsinannin kwamfuta ta iya sun kashe mutane" a Amurka.
Amma Cruz ya ce Pelosi, wanda ya dawo a cikin "Face the Nation" kan senators, "ba fuskanta ba a cikin kowane iri."
"Mafita ta shi ne girman kudi da aka bada wuta akan tsanani kuma aka yi Amurka tashin hankali," ya ce Texas Republican.
"Kuma ga majalisan, ka yi bayani kan biliyan $3 trillion da aka nemi ta sake raba, abin da kake nema ne kawai cin kudi ga masoyiyar ta da kuma ba za a haifar da bikin. Daga cikin haka, matsalar mu gaba ne cewa mutane na Amurka su ci gaba da aiki. Su ka so su ɗaukar harkokin rayuwarsu."
Kungiyar mamakin 'yan majalisar sauran suka dauki matsaloli ga jere a matsayen coronavirus a watan March. Yanzu haka, suka tara irin fashin da za'a zama a matsayin fashin bakwai na coronavirus ya tsare duk da tsare, wanda suke tayar da abubuwan da su ka iya daukar su, wanda suke amfani da takwas. Sun caccakar masa karfe hudu.
A shekarar nan, Manyan Adabin da ke da White House kan Mulkin Mark Meadows da Mnishiri na Kudin Bayar da ke da Treasury Steven Mnuchin suka buga kudi zuwa Capitol Hill domin kawo kayan aiki da masu suna bayan Senet, inda Mnuchin ya ce ga Fox News a wata ranar Asabar cewa bayanai zasu zaba da shi a cikin sanada na babban shugaban Senet Mitch McConnell a watan Litinin.
Ana so ficewa domin masanin shugabanci - da kuma mafi kyau bayanai tsakanin Malaman Rediyo kuma Dimokurati - shi ne tamkar kasa na gano game da fasalin zama shiga cikin masu gano 'yan wasanni da aka kai sabbabin fata mai launi na cewa, wanda ya dace ne yayin nan.
Wani matakai ne kamarku da 'phase four' na coronavirus kuma yan Demokuraɗi ke buƙatar shigar da kira 600 ga faɗin sadauki, inda su kwarewa ne su yi binciken ya zama cikakke don iyaye yadda wadandalin biyan buƙatar su, kuma su ce ba'a san wani mutumin Amurka ya kasance mai zaune a cikin matsalolin.
Cruz ya ce cikin yawan mutanen Amurka mai samun ayyukan karfin ganawa, mafi yawan su suka biya bayan da aka zama masu gudanar da karfin ganawa. Ya kuma ce ya yi magana da masu amfani guda nasa cikin Kasashen Texas wanda suka kara tsaye wadanda suka fara kirayowa.
"Tun daga haka, ba zasu zouna ba saboda gida ta wuraren kasa ta ba su, a wani lokaci, su karbi kudin dubu biyu don taimakawa a gida," ya ce.
Cruz ya ce Kongirashi na fokus da karin kudi game da sake samun abin da zai yiwu masu amfani ya fi son zama aiki akan fifiko zuwa hanyar ƙetaren iri. "akwai wani matsayin tangarar iri da zai ba ni masu su taimake da kai kawai, [nan gaba] wata ƙetare ya kai masa kudi, inda yake ba mu da yawa a cikin ƙashe-kashi masu ci gaba ne da ke zauna a kasa. Yana iya sa mai shigowa aiki," ya ce.
Na rago Donald Trump ran shi huɗu barwaqoyin daga ɗaya dake, amma Mnuchin ya ce ba zai zama arƙiyon 'yan kasar ba, saboda da aka bayyana batu akan bangarorin yana amfani da kansa a tsarin majalisar sa.
Malam Trump ya kaddamar da cewa takardar magoya bayanin nauyi ba zai kasance a cikin bili na gaba ba amma ya tara masu karfi kan Kasuwanci.
Cruz, wanda shi ne ya yi ce ce a ranar Asabar, yayi magana cewa ba za a sami damar tattara sakamakon sa na kowane jumla, ya ce Lahadi ba za su sami irin abu daga cikin majalisar masu Hannu dake kasar Amurika.
Amma kuma ya yi sanadiyyar rikicin katin $3 trillion da aka ƙunsa ta yammacin Kwankwasiyya a Watan Mayu, kuma ya yi nazarin kungiyoyin siyasa na musamman da su zama makiyaya ga wani sanarwa da ke nema ga sojojin kasar a ranar 4 ga watan Nuwamba.
"Yan Demokuraɗo sun yiwu kansu shine don kada Donald Trump ya fuskanci, kuma sun ci gaba da nufin iri irin muhalli a Amurka, sun kada duk madarar a Amurka ya kammala," ya ce.
"Kana sani, Nancy Pelosi ta fada cewa mai kudi da matakin lissafi sun fara aiki. Daga nan ta amince da akai mai kudi da matakin lissafi sun fara aiki."
