Kanadamu na kungiyar Congress Rahul Gandhi ya yi ɗaukar tweet ranar nan a wajen ƙiƙinta mutane ƙasa don kaddamar da jama'a sakamakon jamiyyar BJP a jihar Rajasthan.
Tare da tacciyar alamar #HutuTaDemokradiya, shine ya yi wannan post din Hindia ya yi wa mutanen su "a kuyi kai da gani a matsayin na ci gaba da demokradiya".
Kungiyar Congress ta amfani da cikakken zanga-zangar kusa da yau lahadi ta hanyar zama mafi kyau a jihar Rajasthan, inda hukumomin Ashok Gehlot sun zama matsaloli.
Wani harka ta ce za'a sake a waje gida da kwanan wakarsa wanda ke Amurka a Rashtrapati Bhavan, fadin gida rasul Ram Nath Kovind.
A cikin bidiyo, kungiyar Congress ta ba da BJP na "Dauke da Al'umma da fatawa da biyayya" yayin da duk wani ƙasa ta buga coronavirus.
