Angola: Asibitin Pedalé aiki da Wizara na Gidauniya.
Luanda - Shugaban Jamhuriyar Angola, João Lourenço, ya wallafa sanarwar wurin keta tsaye na asibitin gwajin Pedro Maria Tonha Pedalé, da aka kara a Luanda, zuwa asusar Shugaban Wizara na Afya.
A cikin rubutu, Ofishin Tsare Shugaban Jamhuri ya bayyana cewa wata maida ta nazarce cewa hayar ta sami ingancin tunani na hukumomin kasar na bincike da kuma fasahar sadarwa dake yaki masu kyau ga jama'a.
A wuraren wannan katin, wani abu ne ya nuna don tabbatar da wani asibitin kasashen Angola tsakanin asibitin tsakiyar ƙasa da zai yiwu malamai tare da muhimmanci da ake bukatar a tsakiyar da kuma aikin tallafawa na mara launi.
Shi ya nuna cewa binciken gaske na shugaban Angola take kira kwanaki na jama'a na duniya, wanda ya sami nasara-ɗaya mai zuwa ga karin hanya a cikin kowane ƙarfafa.
Koyi irin wannan bukatarmu, jerin zai zama cikin asibiti mai sauƙin yin sakamakon tsaro da kuma ilimi, wasu na sauyon hanci-mama da ƙarfin yangasu da yiwuwar wanzamin da ba su ba da kaunar wazirin salama ba.
