Da yawan 30 mahaifi sun yi lasisin Coronavirus a cikin banki daya a Tamil Nadu.
Kusa da sanarwa 38 kungiyoyin a cikin bankin tarayyar a kasa a al'umma na Tiruchirappalli, Tamil Nadu, sun sami coronavirus, amincin banki da haɗin kasa sun ce.
Sannan ta hanyar ma'aikatar sa, girman 'yan kudi da suka ziyara banki sun kasa kayan aiki da su zabi yadda suke fitar da coronavirus.
Kwadan da ake zargin mahaifinsa a matsayin ma'aikata duk ya mutu sosai ne daga COVID-19.
Wasu mutanen da duka suka danganta ne suka nuna bayan da yankin cikin kungiyar tarihi na haraji ta halarci a cikin banki ta zuwa ga wani kimar harkokin lafiya, yace ma masu shirin ta.
Ma'aikata banki na farko suka ce ana koma kwayoyin disinfection ta kasa, kuma aiki na banki za'a iya bisa ranar gobe.
