Kanye West na bayyana fatan alheri game da mahaifa Kim Kardashian bayan bayanin gurbanka.
Kanye West ya yi gaishe da kimin matarsa Kim Kardashian ta sassan za a bayyana ta tare da "hanyoyin gida."
Rapper ya bayyana a ranar a Arewacin Carolina cewa sun yi shawarar da ya fadi gida da mahaifiyar aure suka nemi.
Bayan watan da aka yi kuskuren lokacin da ya bayyana matakai game da mahaifinsa da 'yarsa, West yana tsaya tweet yana barin tsari.
Tarihi: Fasaha kuma ta ruwaito cikin wata sanarwa bayan an kawo kan ma'aikata a lokacin da Justin Bieber yayi ziyarar zuwa \*ranch*\* din da ke yamma a Wyoming.   (Note: the word "ranch" does not have a direct translation in Hausa, so it is written in English with a Hausa transcription)
