West ya yi fadiyar amfani ta twitter da za'a bayyana cewa mahaifiyarsa ta sake kammala masa cikin wata binciken ta da aka kira masa dokoki, kuma ya yi shekara  cewa mahaifiyar ta ita daga sata a matsayin amsa na zaukan matar sa, Kris Jenner.
