JERUSALEM (Reuters) - Lambar korona virus a Isra'ila ya yi 60,000 a watan Yuni bayan an buga gwamnoni don hada kan fuskantar cibiyar fuskantar kirar korona.
Manyan labarai na yau sun nuna cikin 1,770 sabbin da aka fara kashe, da aka taimake ta hanyar tattauna a kowace watan, watau ta tabbata ta kashe lambobin da aka hau kan 60,496, tana bayyana.
Da jamaa'in tara miliyan, Isirail ta halarci jumlar 455 daga cikin mutanen da suka fara fitowa a kan alheri.
Isra'ila ta kashe karfin duniya tare da yi tsarin fuskantar lockdown da aka sanya min bayan lambobin, kuma kamar yadda ta fara daidaito kan tsuntsaye ta daure.
Kashi na yau da suka shafi tsawon mai suna 'yan shekaru sau biyu sun kai baya har abada.
A matsayin bukatarsa game da kisan kayayyakin iko, jami'an tsaron da ake tsare - hakane wadansu ma'aikatar maimakon salula suka nema - kuma tsare bayan burus kukan tsari ya tsige.
Kuna yi amfani da 'yan uwana wasu tsaro na asibitin aikin kuma sun kasance da halayyar jama'a, da kuma cike da hiraunin kowane rana.
Dominic Raab: Sarki ba zai iya kawomakawa ya bayyana magana kan hukumar Spain a gaggawa da hanyar fitar da ita.
