Waziri suka kirkiri a shekarar shekara da lingen biyu da yaushe, cewa mutun da suka samu cutar Hispania kuma sha'awar su aka koma tsakanin shekaru goma ashirin don yi lokacin wadanda suka ji lallai ba su taba koya ba.
Girman kasar ne a cikin jerin binciken da aka fi sani damar ziyarci a gida da ke cikin aro musamman ta yamma da tsuntsaye na coronavirus, amma a lokacin da aka kusantar da sunayen dandali na coronavirus sau da yawa, yaji kama mutum saboda hannu ta biyu na cutar coronavirus.
A ranbi a lahadi, Wazirin Baya ya matsayi tallafin kai tsakanin baki daya a tashin hankali da nuna cutar daukar hankalin ana kasa.
Ya ce zai shawo hali a rana ta baki na daya "kuma mu halarci qarar komai kamar yadda mukeyi."
"Ba za mu iya yi gaskiya ta hanyar yi hankali kamar haka," yace.
Muna iya samu kasuwanci, kiyayya kuma kyan gudanar da aikin mugayawa, ga yadda zamu iya aiki, musamman da aka koyar da tsohon kasuwanci, ko ya dace yawan jama'a daga kasar Espain amma ko kuma wani kasashe, inda zaka samu cewa, fada aiki muna iya yi.
Wannan yana buƙata bayan da mu san yadda ake fuskantar kasuwanci bisa shekaru biyu a cikin UK, da yake, za mu bayar da gurgun samaniya ta wannan lokaci kuma kada akan ci gaba da mai hakuri.
Malamai na shekarar tsakanin kasashen Spain da suka shiga cikin karantinobi sosai.
Matsiyar an yi bayan da Spain ta wuce 900 da aka sabon yau bayan zama mafi sanya da Covid-19 bayan ran biyu.
Waziri na jamiyya ne ya qara da cewa an kunna su fiye da lokaci don kaga ko kawo mabiyan tsaro.
"Ya fahimci cewa wannan ya samar da kumallo akan mata wadda suke Spain ko sun fi kalmar wa ko in yi aiki amma zamu iya yin nazarin makiyaya mai jifa-jifan hanya da dama domin samun amfani don Birtaniya," ya ce.
"Mu yi kara tattalin arziki a matsayin fuskantar sauran al'umma da kuma tsare shi don matsayin fuskantar a Biritaniya."
Yara sun fito daga Gatwick Airport akan subuhan lahira a ranbi Sataday bayan tarihin bayanin (PA).
Shadow Waziri na Iyali Jonathan Ashworth ya tsaya masa daci da tsarin sarkin kasar cewa "tafi kusan shambolic" a yin nasara ga wani shiryar da aka kirkiro.
Yace cikin Downing Street bambanci na amfani ne ya kai wa mutanen hutawa "yanzuni da kuka fiye da wuya."
Mai martaba Labour ya ce ga Sophy Ridge: "Ina fahimtar cewa kuna da wata kuskure amma, binciken da aka yi a ran 24 na cikin lokaci yana da hankali."
Akwai masu karbar rakiya a Spani a yanzu masu samun mamba da kudurin, akwai mutane da suke neman haliyar rakiyar karbar a Spani da kuma jumhuriyar Canary kamar Tenerife suna mamba da kudurin, kuma ba su san da suka ba su sami sakamako biyu na kwana.
Sarki ya ce duk da haka, 'muna son masanin muna halarci.'
"Tsarin da wannan tsarin ya yi a lokacin 24 na dembi yana da abin da aka karyata ne a wurin gwajin gwaji."
Me kakeyi mutanen da suka sha'awar Spaniya a cikin jerin karantawa ya zamo don mutane da suka haifar da sauri?
Ya kai wuraren wazirai su bayyana "zahiriyya" a matsayin dai in za su ba su taimaka da ilmantar da za a sa su a matsayin maganar damar su amfani da ayyukan kuɗin su idan maziyar su bai tabbatar da kuɗi a yanzu.
Yace duk da haka an bukatar bayanan mai raba damar yin cututtukan al'amuran da suka kasance a Spain wanda suka sakawa tsakanin shekara, don su ci gaba da cutar jama'a su ne cikakken.
"Ta hanyar da wannan tsarin da aka gudanar a bayyana ne zai sake gwada duka," ya tona asirin.
Malamin Raab ya ce ba za a iya maimakon wadanda su tabbatar da hadin mutuwa saboda ilmantarwa ta hanyar masana'antu, kamar yadda suka yi addu'a akan sanyin karbar da su ka fada da milinki jiki.
Ya ce: "Munyi canje-canje - shari'a ta canza kan al'umma da waka - kuma babban birnin muna lura da mu daidai abin da zanyi yadda za ka rasa sundaya sabbin ma'aikata musamman ga wani abokan zama da yake sunan suna ne ke shirin suna.”
"Idan wani mutum ya yi maganin shari'a akan karantin da kuma isolating din sarari tare da ke so, ba zai iya samun zargin ko ganewa kudi a kowane lokaci."
QB Herbert kuma watan 4 na cutar sun ceto ta Chargers.
COSTA MESA, Calif. (AP) - Los Angeles Chargers sun dakatar da farko-pal, inda aka buga quarterback Justin Herbert, kuma sun ga irin abubuwan biyu a cikin taron sunayen da suka buga.
Chargers sun fadada suluhu da kariyar tarihi a rana Asabar lamarin da suka sha da ginshi da abubuwa a cikin gasar ci gaba ta gargajiya.
Daga cikin Herbert, wanda aka zaɓa tare da sabon shekaru na shida, kungiyar ta kan rubuta sharrarorin Joe Reed (gwargwadon biyu) da KJ Hill (gwargwadon bakwai) tare da Alohi Gilman wanda aka zaɓa tare da shekaru na shida da ɗari na shida.
Sune ma za su shirya suna da kwarewarsa tare da Kenneth Murray Jr. da kuma matsala na jirgin ruwa Joshua Kelley, wanda aka zauna a tattaunawa na farko.
Herbert ya fara kaga kowane game bayan Oregon, ya sami hadin kari ga 29-13 tare da 10,541 passing yards da 108 total touchdowns.
Ya kara shugaban Yan uwana zuwa 'yan harkokin Pac-12 a shekarar da suka gabata, ya fitar da 32 kudin farko da shida da bakwai a shekarun 14.
Ya ƙaura ya kama irin sako da kungiyar ya gama Wisconsin a cikin Rose Bowl, inda ya gudu saman kwalewa da ya fadi a kowane layin sako akan sunayen MVP.
Herbert zai iya taimaka da Tyrod Taylor da aka hada shi don zama mutum mafi ɗaya a taka.
Chargers sun yi karɓar lambobin saboda Philip Rivers ya tara tsakanin kudi bayan da ya sami nauyi tsakanin shanu bayan shekaru 14 ya aiki.
Murray ya sami lambarka na farko bayan Los Angeles ta dauki karshen gabansa tare da New England. Yayin da aka kai wa cikinsa lamba guda biyu da ukuwar gaban.
Shi ne talla ta biyu da ayyukanshi ga America a ranar season a nan bayan ya yi dasewa a cikin kungiyar Sooners ta gudanar da 102 cikakken ayyukan, wanda aka dade 69 ayyuka-takwas.
Kanye West ya ce ya zama maɓallin Joe Biden "daga karatu" - RT USA News.
Dafatan rubutaccen mahaifiyar shi na Twitter, motsa jiki rap enigma Kanye West ya kara tsanani suka yi akan yin amfani daga yin taimako sakamakon shi zuwa babban shafin sarauta, ya ce ya zai iya samu tsantsan ginshi ta Joe Biden a matsayin rayuwarsa domin ba a san shi ba.
Bayan an nema sha'awar album saboda yadda ya yi bayyana cewa ya nufin fatawa da mijiya Kim Kardashian domin biyu sanannen shekara, Kanye West ya sa hannunsa a kan harkokin shugaban kasa na 2020 a ranar Asabar, a bangaren da aka rubuta ta hanyar bangaren tsarin "ZAN TABBATAR DA BIDEN DAGA CIGIN KAN".
Idan ta kasance tsakanin yauza-yauza game da gudanar da shugaban kasa, za'a iya yin sace-sace na rubuta karanta saboda kawai ita zai dace masa suna, ko kuma ko zuwa yanzu ba za'a iya halicci wani irin tarihi ba.
An gano rap na cewa ya gudanar da shi a ranar 4 ga watan July, domin ya kammala lokacin da aka daure ta hanyar gudanar da shi a tsakanin yankunan shekaru shidda.
Duk da haka, West ya tafi araha da ta rasu a cikin Binciken Tsare Tsohon Shugaban Sarewa (FEC), kuma ya samar da sunan shi a matakai a Oklahoma.
Ko dai yanzu ya fara gudanar da shugaban kasa tsakanin wata jirgin samari, a ranar ta juma'a, inda ya yi albashi tare da sarrafa aikinshi a bayan jama'a da yafi kai ga jirgin samari, ya rasa hutuwar sa tsakanin maikarfi ko alamu.
West ya zo ya fi haramta kan aborshin, yana jin wasa akan addinin Kristi ya ce zai kare shawarar wannan kalamai a jama'a, ya kuma ce ya fi sanya al'umma cewa "na da tsoron Allah".
Kuma a wajen rt.com Kanye West ya ce ya zama aka nema Kim Kardashian, ya fice cewa ta da mama'i-magana 'Kris Jong Un' sunyi kuɗin farauta.
Wannan abunda aka ce zai danganci, da kuma takardun matakan labarai da suka rubuta a gidan tsaron da suke magana game da shi ne kuma matsaloli na da aure tsakanin quewasu, ko kuma jami'an tsaron.
Anyway, sauri wani saiti ya tuna West a biyu na cikin waje dukkanin hular 2, baki daya bayan kowa a jama'a, duk da haka da wata alama bayan kowane jama'a, Jo Jorgensen na Partin Libertaria, da kuma biyu ba tsafta bayan Partin Hausa, Howie Hawkins.
Ko kuma wani lokacin da ba zai iya damar yin auku takwas ne cikin sayan Joe Biden da yasa'i, a yanzu kuma za'a iya kawo kowane 'yan wasan daga cikin 'yan Biden don amma yayi Trump ya kammala fata kasar biyar - watau suke ganin cewa wannan shi ne sanin shi.
Koreya ta Arewa ta sanar da hanyar jefa harkokin kashe korona na Covid-19
Kim Jong-un wanda shi ne kafa kasar North Korea ya samu matsala ya nuna karo na politburo a cikin watan Disamba bayan wani mutum wanda ayyukansa cikin jihar tare da Covid-19 ya dawo daga Kudancin Korea Ta Kudu a wannan Wata watau, saka fili ne a cewa manhajar sauye-sauyen tattalin arziki.
Idan da aka daure, zai fi ta tatafi ya faru da sanarwar jam'iyyar  kudu ta Arewa Koreya, wanda yasa haka aka bai wa yanzu cewa yanzu littafan kasa ba su sami ta da fama da tsarin korona.
Kim ya fice wani hali mai amfani a ciki da lardin Kaesong da ke jirgin birnin da kuka karya talla, ya yi magana cewa an 'sake kira kimanin matsala wanda ya mayar da virus ta shahara ya dawo gida,' karkara littafin harkokin kasa KCNA ya ruwaito.
Sannan akwai bayanai cewa KCNA, wani mutum da ya gudana daga Korea ta Kudu sun fara tace bayan watanni uku bisa shafukan da ke jiran kungiyar Korea ta Arewacin sama da dama mai alamun Covid-19.
"KCNA ta ce 'Zabuka mai dauke da shugaban Kaesong wanda ya koma nan ta kudu matasa zuwa kudancin kudu kacacin uku, wani abu wanda aka sha'awar da kansa yana sha suspishin cewa ya rasu ne ya ce."  Note: This is a rough translation to Hausa and may not accurately convey the original meaning.
KCNA ba don bayyana domin in da ake gwadawa dan Adam wata kusan, amma yayi magana akan "harshe mai matsakaicin ba a samu da makiyaya kusan ba a zamanin biyar da kuma damuwa," aiki da wata kwarewa, masu zaman kansu suka rinka shirya dan majalisa da suka sami kira ga dan haka da ya fi kashe dan haka ta da koya.
Koreya ta Arewa ta sami matsayin sunayen coronavirus da kuma saman jami'an tsarin son wajen rufe abinci daga Rasha da sauran dokokin da ke cikin zama, kuma ta rike kewaye ce wayanda ke da kwamfuta bayan gari.
Saukar da miliyan yan'uwa a cikin hukumar sirriya sun taimake su gagarum, amma bayan haka tsari na samu kasashen.
A lokacin da aka fara karfe, Shimiyar Koreya ta kuma zama yadda ta zama takarar da aka nema kan mutane da suka fadi zaben marasa a Kudancin Koreya ta Arewa ta hanyar gani da amsar yin matsayin "gashi na mutum" kuma ganin kada aka kare da kasan samar da suke kira 'yan fashewa da kuma rawa da suke kirkirar wani abin da za su samu a Koreya ta Arewa.
Kim ya yi takardar zargi akan kungiyoyin askari a harsashin yankin inda mutum ya yi wahala ta hanyar goge wani matsalar tare da kai tsaye, lafiya da mafita da aka bukaci ne.
Paul Pogba ya bayyana abinda za a iya yi akan rayuwarsa bayan Man Utd ya ci gaba da gudana da Champions League.
Manchester United star Paul Pogba ya tabbatar da cewa zai taimaka maka zama a kungiyar wannan kakar taken da Red Devils sun taimaka maka maki na biyu.
Wannan matan 2-0 daga Leicester ya bayyana cewa United ta kammala cikin uku ta tsakiya, a karshe na Chelsea ta da Frank Lampard.
United sun kasance adadin 14 a sauran wannan lokaci 12 na daga cikin matasan Leicester amma zata samu damar  kasancewa daga cikin wannan lokacin da suka samo sashen mai bada lamba cikin kungiyar.
Pogba sun samu matsalar shi ya tara shara ta kasuwar a wannan kauye bayan da aka ce dauko ne sabon majalisar bayan shekaru biyu.
Duk lokacin da akwai cutar, kasashen kulabu suna tsira da kuma babu wanda ya iya shiga karo da fasali na Pogba domin cewa ya dauki shi daga Old Trafford.
Wani bayani ya taɓatar da dama ya ayyana Pogba a shekara mafi ƙasashen da suka faru saɗen shi, kuma suna shaɗawa shi daidai.
Da yake, Faransanci yana nuna cewa zai taimaka tare da kungiyar ta hanyar bayyana akan wannan kananan da aka yi bayan kungiyar tana dubawa hannun 2-0 ta hannunshi ta Instagram.
Jama'a sun nema cewa Pogba ya nuna fushi akan zuwa mai tsanani na kungiyar, amma an kammala wadanda suka samu cewa hakan ya yi muku labarin dauke da maimakawa cewa zai zama a kungiyar da suke magana da kuma kowa na turai a ko da yaushe a gaba.
Pogba yana daga shekaru daya inda ya koma a sama na fili, kuma kungiyar tayi muku sauki don zama 12 watanni wanda zai sa shi a daga cikin shekaru biyu.
Yunayted sun nemi cikin kawo kashi Pogba da su ke so duk bayan kakar sabuwar kakar.
Pogba, domin samunsa, yana da kyakkyawan maza a kungiyar da ya kasance yadda zaƙi da fitowa da Bruno Fernandes.
Kuma, gwamnatoci na Portugal ya zama cikakken 'yan kwallon kafa a Old Trafford da kuma gaji da wannan ya ba Pogba shi ne ya rusa tsantsar kaɗan na közawa mai fuskantar hanya, wanda ke kara kara fanin sa.
